00:14.540 --> 00:16.120
♪ Plenty of polka dots ♪

00:18.250 --> 00:20.210
♪ Get those puppies! ♪

00:20.210 --> 00:21.880
♪ Can't catch
a furry flurry ♪

00:21.880 --> 00:23.620
♪ Running in a blurry hurry ♪

00:26.120 --> 00:27.040
♪ Get those puppies! ♪

00:28.420 --> 00:30.710
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:30.710 --> 00:32.250
♪ Canines on the run ♪

00:32.250 --> 00:34.120
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:34.120 --> 00:35.580
♪ Them doggone dogs are fun ♪

00:35.580 --> 00:37.000
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:37.000 --> 00:39.620
♪ Without fail you'll wind up
chasing your tail ♪

00:39.620 --> 00:41.620
♪ What's the harm
in revelrous adventures ♪

00:41.620 --> 00:43.540
♪

00:43.540 --> 00:44.750
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:46.000 --> 00:47.210
♪ Life's just a bed of roses ♪

00:47.210 --> 00:48.380
♪ 1-0-1 ♪

00:48.380 --> 00:50.580
♪ Fast friends
